Probabilistic Sensitivity Analysis (PSA) parameters

Source: R/data.R
l_psa_parameters.Rd

This list contains the parameters used for a probabilistic sensitivity analysis (PSA). Each parameter includes the distribution function and the necessary parameters for that distribution.

Usage

l_psa_parameters

Format

A list with the following components:

body_weight

A list with the following elements:

dist_func

Distribution function, here "rnorm".

dist_params

A list of parameters for the distribution:

mean

Mean of the normal distribution.

sd

Standard deviation of the normal distribution.

GD2_unit_price

A list with the following elements:

dist_func

Distribution function, here "rgamma".

dist_params

A list of parameters for the distribution:

shape

Shape parameter of the gamma distribution.

scale

Scale parameter of the gamma distribution.

TT_unit_price

A list with the following elements:

dist_func

Distribution function, here "rgamma".

dist_params

A list of parameters for the distribution:

scale

Scale parameter of the gamma distribution.
